# HireHub Onboarding Portal - Environment Variables
#
# This is a client-side-only application. No environment variables are required.
#
# Data Persistence:
# - Application state is stored in localStorage for persistent data
#   (e.g., onboarding progress, user preferences).
# - sessionStorage is used for temporary session-scoped data
#   (e.g., form drafts, transient UI state).
#
# No backend API or external services are needed to run this application.
#
# If you extend this project with API integrations in the future,
# add Vite-compatible environment variables below using the VITE_ prefix:
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api
# VITE_APP_TITLE=HireHub Onboarding Portal